    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 115</em>, <em>PRPG Core Rulebook pg. 463</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> moderate transmutation <strong>CL</strong> 8th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> shield quality; <strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>A shield with this special ability is designed to perform a shield bash. A <em>bashing </em>shield deals damage as if it were a weapon of two size categories larger (a Medium light shield thus deals 1d6 points of damage and a Medium heavy shield deals 1d8 points of damage). The shield acts as a +1 weapon when used to bash. Only light and heavy shields can have this ability.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>bull's strength</em>; <strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus</p>",
